(8, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Beta 1 has been released on 2011.12.01', '&lt;p&gt;As a result of several weeks serious prepartion, the brand new Lively 24*7 Service Beta 1 has been released on 2011.12.01. And we are trying our best to release the final version by the end of this month. For more detail about it, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2011-12-01 14:13:05', 0),
(9, 1, 'A new service called &quot;Subscribe Mobile Phone Number&quot; has been released', '&lt;p&gt;Did you ever met phone reverification roadblock when you added friends for your Facebook accounts? How to unblock this account if you didn''t grasp the phone number in your hand which belongs to your Facebook account? Wait and hope it changes other kinds of roadblock or just give up this account? Now I am glad to introduce our subscribe mobile phone number service for you. This service can help you solve the above problem. Please refer to Step 4 &quot;My Service&quot;--&amp;gt;&quot;Subscribe Mobile Phone Number&quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2011-12-05 15:13:11', 0),
(10, 1, 'Add a new service &quot;Add Targeted Friends&quot; on the left vertical navigation', '&lt;p&gt;The page of new service &quot;Add Targeted Friends&quot; is under development at present. This service is aimed to help customers who want to add targeted friends by us, and then comfirm the friend request by yourself. We are trying our best to release this service as eary as we can, looking forward to your patience and support!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2011-12-10 09:53:59', 0),
(11, 1, 'Happy Christmas Eve!', 'Christmas day is coming! Wish all of you have a wonderful christmas holiday! And we are providing special offers to all customers during the chirstmas period. Please refer to our &quot;Special Offer&quot; page to get more detail. ', 1, 0, '2011-12-24 10:57:39', 0),
(12, 1, 'New Year with new hope is coming!', '&lt;p&gt;Thanks all the customers great support with our product and service in the past year. We will try our best to improve the software and service better and better. Wish you have a new start in the new year! And our 24*7 sales support are having the new year holidays from 1st Jan to 3rd Jan, if you have any questions during these days, please send email to support@livelyservice.com, we will reply you when we are back from our holidays. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks a lot!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-01 05:00:06', 0),
(13, 1, 'Facebook new timeline interface will be support in the FFAP in the near days', '&lt;p&gt;Due to Facebook begins to change new timeline interface for all the accounts/pages. FFAP haven''t support this new feature at the current version. However, we have added this item in our TODO list, our tech team are trying their best to fix this problem as soon as possible. The new update of FFAP is expected to launch in the near days. Looking forward to your patience and support!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-04 07:00:58', 0),
(14, 1, 'Advance notice for the brand new Lively 24*7 Service Beta 2', '&lt;p&gt;In order to perfect our service, our support and tech team try their best to improve our customer service and order deal system these days, and there will be some updates for the services accoding to these changes. After two weeks preparation, the brand new Lively 24*7 Service Beta 2 will be released next days. Please pay close attention to our latest news for this new update.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-18 10:01:37', 0),
(15, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Beta 2 has been released on 2012.01.21', '&lt;p&gt;The brand new Lively 24*7 Service Beta 2 has been released on 2012.01.21. And the final verison will be released early next month. For more detail about it, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/ If you have any question or suggestion about our service, please feel free to contact our support team at any time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-21 09:02:18', 0),
(16, 1, 'Non-standard related service have to be postponed starting next month', '&lt;p&gt;Since we spend all our time on the standard Facebook service at present. We may have not enough time to manage Non-standard Facebook related service project, such as &quot;Send Direct Messages&quot;, &quot;Invite Page Fans&quot;, &quot;Post Application Review&quot;...etc. However, these kinds of related services have been developed, we will start these services once we completed our standard Facebook service next month. Looking forward to your patient and support. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-28 12:03:11', 0),
(17, 1, 'Voice verification was removed from Facebook', '&lt;p&gt;There are two ways to verify Facebook accounts with phone numbers, they are &quot;Call Me&quot; and &quot;Send me a text message&quot;. But the &quot;Call Me&quot; method was removed by Facebook, that means you only can verify Facebook accounts with text messages from now on. However, you still can use &quot;Call Me&quot; to re-verify your Facebook account if you''ve added a phone number for your account before.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-02-05 12:03:45', 0),
(18, 1, 'The re-verification service will be postponed for a period of time', '&lt;p&gt;Since the mobile phone signal is unsteady due to some reasons at present, we can''t receive the verification code from Facebook by the phone numbers. So the re-verification service will be postponed for a periof of time. We are very sorry to bring you any trouble, looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-02-16 17:04:27', 0),
(19, 1, 'Other country''s phone numbers are expected to use for PVA verification', '&lt;p&gt;In order to replenish our PVA stock, we decide to look for some mobile phone number suppliers to solve this problem. We''ve found a Philippines mobile phone number supplier which can offer long-term Philippines mobile phone numbers, so we will use these mobile phone numbers to verify Facebook accounts. And also we are still trying to look for more mobile phone number suppliers for us to improve our service better and better.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-02-20 18:05:06', 0),
(20, 1, 'The Final Version of LivelyService have been Released', '&lt;p&gt;Due to recent changes in the software and our service, we have modified some related parts of our service, such as FAQ, Policy, Working Follow and so on. We highly recommend customers to refer to the related parts of each service if you have any questions about our service. Or contact our 24*7 sales support for any questions or suggestion, make sure you make full clear about our service before placing the order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-02-21 18:05:51', 0),
(21, 1, 'PVAs are still out of stock since can''t be verified smoothly', '&lt;p&gt;Due to the Chinese mobile phone signals is still not very steady, our FB PVAs are out of stock at present. So please pay attention to the &quot;Important Notice&quot; on our &quot;PVA Service&quot; page before placed your order. However, our tech team are focusing on this problem, they will solve this case as soon as possible after found a long-term mobile phone supplier. Looking forward to your patient and support.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-03-01 16:06:24', 0),
(22, 1, 'A new update on FFAP will come out soon', '&lt;p&gt;Since Facebook changes some parameters these days, some features may show the same error when running: &quot;Received an unknown error from facebook.com. Can''t make sure whether it''s a warning message, so let''s just stop this account for security reason. Our test team will check out this unknow error as soon as possible.&quot; Our tech team are handling this issue at present, the new update is expected to release within 2 days. Sorry to cause you any trouble.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-03-19 19:07:02', 0),
(23, 1, 'Facebook FriendAdder Pro 3.0.0 built on 2012.03.24.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;There are several bugs occored in FFAP since facebook changed some parameters the other days. Our tech team have checked and found out the problem in time, and also add some new features in the new update. Please get the detail information about &quot;What''s New&quot; in the latest version from http://livelyservice.com/facebook_friendadder_pro_new.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-03-24 12:07:38', 0),
(24, 1, 'Facebook FriendAdder Pro 3.0.0 built on 2012.03.26.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;Some bugs are fixed in the new update of FFAP, for more detail information about this update, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/facebook_friendadder_pro_new.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-03-26 20:08:22', 0),
(25, 1, 'We will be on Chinese Qingming Festival Holidays for 3 days', '&lt;p&gt;The Chinese Traditional Qingming Festival is coming, we will have 3 days holidays from April 2nd to April 5th. Your orders won''t be delivered since our support team will be offline during this period. We are very sorry to cause you any trouble.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-03-30 16:08:55', 0),
