(27, 1, 'Important nocice on &quot;Unlock Friend Photo Verification&quot; Service', '&lt;p&gt;You may meet an error when tried to unlock the friend photo verification for your FB accounts manually on Facebook. It shows &quot;No verification methods are currently available&quot; after you selected all the friends'' photos. So we aslo can''t bypass this kind of roadblcok for the accounts until Facebook fixs this bug. Please have a close eye on our &quot;Latest News&quot;, we will inform you here at once if this service is abailable. Thanks for your patient and support.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-04-19 16:10:12', 0),
(28, 1, 'A new update will be released within days.', '&lt;p&gt;As there are some changes on facebook these days, it causes some features in FFAP can''t work. Our tech team are working hard on these bugs, and we will try our best to release a new version to keep the program working well. Sorry to cause you any trouble and thanks for your patience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-05-07 17:10:43', 0),
(29, 1, 'FFAP 2.3.0 built on 2011.05.10.01 has been released.', '&lt;p&gt;What''s news in the new updates:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI. Features Improved:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Support security question and second email in the default account format;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Bugs Fixed:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Fixed a problem of failed to check out phone number while checking accounts;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Fixed a problem of failed to Add/Message Online/Targeted Friends by sex filter;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Fixed a problem of failed to find other''s friends in &quot;Find Targeted Friends&quot;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Fixed a problem of failed to message accounts'' friends in &quot;Message Online friends&quot;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Fixed a problem of failed to share any updates in &quot;Share Wall Updates&quot;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Fixed a problem of failed to bypass any kind of checkpoint while logging accounts;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Fixed a problem of failed to set bad ip accounts as login failed while checking accounts;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. Fixed some unknown error problems because of facebook.com changes in all related features;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-05-10 06:11:41', 0),
(30, 1, 'A important Notice to the customer who placed a custom order from us', '&lt;p&gt;Please make sure your paypal account is normal after you sent us the money for your custom project. Cause Paypal may hold your account temporarily by some insecurity factors to keep your account safe. Usually we will contact you once we receive the related notification from paypal. Please solve the problem with us as soon as possible, cause your project won''t be started until we receive your money. Thanks for your kindly cooperation and great support.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-05-16 19:13:26', 0),
(31, 1, 'Good news on PVA verification service', '&lt;p&gt;Under several days studying on the online verification system, our tech team develop this project finally, and implement it successfully. That means our PVA service as well as all the services related verification will be recovered in the following days.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-05-22 18:01:44', 0),
