(59, 1, 'Holiday Announcement and Special Offers', '&lt;p&gt;We are sorry to notice you that we will have Chinese Mid-Autumn Day and National Day holidays from Sep 29th 4:00 PM to Oct 6th 8:30 AM (GMT 8). If you need to contact our support during the holidays, please feel free to email support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as possible when we are back. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn order to express our regret about the long holidays, we are providing special offers for you, especially our PVA accounts. More detail, please refer to &quot;Special Offers&quot;. The price may go up when we are back from holidays. Hurry up,Don''t miss it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-09-25 16:18:06', 0),
