(61, 1, 'The upgrade version of Lively 24*7 Service has been released on 2012.10.10', '&lt;p&gt;We are so excited to tell you that we have finally developed the All-In-One solution for Facebook Marketing! It turns up with a new layout and brings in some new content, such as &quot;Daily Tips&quot;, &quot;Special Offers&quot;, &quot;FAQ&quot;.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn addition, To celebrate Facebook FriendAdder added to Lively 24*7 Service. We launch limited special offer for Facebook FriendAdder: Only $1 to get Facebook FriendAdder life time license. Only 100 copies available! For more details, please refer to the &quot;Special Offers&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-10 16:22:51', 0),
(62, 1, 'Create Facebook accounts with 4000+ targeted friends by Yourself', '&lt;p&gt;Do you want to create accounts with thousands of Global/Niches/GEO/Custom targeted friends by yourself? If yes, the &quot;30 Days Action Plan&quot; ebook is the key to guide you success. This is the first eBook from our professional technical support team. It''s such a powerful and workable eBook! The original price is $99, buy now you are able to get it at a really amazing price!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOnly last 5 days for this limited special offer, please hurry up if you are interested! For more details about the amazing price, please refer to the Special Offers page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-25 16:23:42', 0),
(63, 1, 'Daily Tip videos of Facebook marketing are updating from now on', '&lt;p&gt;For your better understanding of our software and facebook marketing, our tech support team take lots of time to make some useful tip videos base on their rich experience on how to better usage of facebook accounts and software. The aspects which it refers to facebook accounts, proxy, roadblcok, software and marketing.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe will release one tip everyday in the Daily Tips section in Lively 24*7 Service. You can log on the Daily Tips section to check for new tips which would be an inspiration on your facebook marketing and help you achieve your success early. Please refer to the Daily Tips page to check the first tip video &quot;How to manage thousands of accounts conveniently?&quot; today.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-26 16:24:22', 0),
(64, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support team are having meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;Our 24*7 Support team are having an important meeting from 3PM to 5PM. If you have any question during this time, please leave us meesage by online messagers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes. Sorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-29 16:25:08', 0),
(65, 1, 'Notice in the &quot;Bypass Mobile Phone Re-verification&quot; feature', '&lt;p&gt;As you may know, you can bypass the mobile phone re-verification roadblock for your PVAs by the feature &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot; in software FFA/FFAP. But usually it may take you lots of time to wait the codes from us to bypass the accounts. To solve this problem, we would like to sort out all the SIM cards of phone numbers in orders. After that, you can bypass this kind of roadblock for PVA much faster.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe will try our best to finish all the work within 24 hours, there may be some delay for this feature during this time. If you fail to bypass, please try it after 24 hours. Sorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-30 16:25:42', 0),
(66, 1, 'New method to get IDs of target groups', '&lt;p&gt;As you know, if you want to find/add friends from a specific group with the software, you have to find the group''s ID. But according the facebook changes, sometimes you can''t find the group ID by old method. The new method to get IDs from a group is as follows:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) Double click one account in the &quot;Manage Accounts&quot; dialog;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) Type keyword in the search bar, and select one specific group, open it;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3) Click &quot;Photos&quot; on the top, and find &quot;Photos and Videos&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4) There is a same string numbers behind each picture when you stay your mouse on the picture.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSince the inner browser doesn''t support right click, you need to write down the string number and paste it to replace the default group ID in the software. If you use outer browser, right click one of picture, select &quot;Copy short link&quot;, paste it in the search bar, then you can copy the group ID.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-10-31 16:26:37', 0),
(67, 1, 'Choose the most trustful customer service staff for you in a settled time', '&lt;p&gt;We publish the working time of our 24*7 Sales Support team in &quot;Contact Us&quot; page. You can choose and talk with your trustful customer service staff in a settled time from now on. For example, if you have any application or important suggestion, you can contact the Team Leader Jack at 06:00-12:00 AM.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-01 16:43:23', 0),
(68, 1, 'Happy Halloween!', '&lt;p&gt;What sort of traditions do you have for Halloween? What are you dressing up as this year? And are you actually going trick-or-treating? Wish all of you have a great Halloween!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-01 16:44:00', 0),
(69, 1, 'Free PVAs for FFA and FFAP customers', '&lt;p&gt;We are providing free PVAs for our FFA and FFAP customers. You can get 3 free PVAs with your FFA/FFAP license. Free account quantity is limited, please hurry up to apply for the accounts which your most want. For more details, please refer to &quot;Specail Offers&quot; Page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-02 16:45:26', 0),
(70, 1, 'We are having weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;Our 24*7 Support team are having weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. If you have any question during this time, please leave us meesage by online messagers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes. Sorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-05 16:48:43', 0),
(71, 1, '$1 to get Facebook FriendAdder lifetime license and free PVAs to test', '&lt;p&gt;In order to thanks for customers'' great support, we would like to provide another 300 copies of Facebook FriendAdder (FFA) lifetime license. With FFA license, you can also apply three free PVAs from us to test with the software and our PVA service. For more detail, please refer to the &quot;Specail Offers&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-07 16:50:31', 0),
(72, 1, 'Add more Free PVAs into our stock', '&lt;p&gt;Due to too many customers request free PVAs these days, we decide to add more free PVAs to rich the free account stock today. Accounts are limited, please hurry up to contact us for your free PVAs. Don''t miss it!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-08 09:15:32', 0),
(73, 1, 'How to bypass re-verification for FFA/FFAP user', '&lt;p&gt;For FFA and FFAP user, There is no need to send accounts to us, please follow these steps to bypass the re-verification roadblock.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Open FFA or FFAP, click Facebook menu -&amp;gt; Preferences;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Tick the option Auto Re-Verify PVA accounts, and click OK to save it;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Back to manage accounts table, select the pink accounts, click &quot;Start To&quot; button-&amp;gt; Bypass Login Problems -&amp;gt;click OK button to run this feature;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. After we input the confirm code in system, your accounts will bypass this re-verification roadblock automatically.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur 24*7 orders support team will check the system all the time. If there is a phone number need to be re-verify. We will find the sim card and get the confirm code from equipment. To shorten the waiting time for customers, we have chosen to prioritize this.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-10 09:16:34', 0),
(74, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support team are having meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. Our 24*7 sales support will be offline from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8), and technical support team will be offline from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8). If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@livelyservice.com&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;support@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes. Sorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-12 09:17:44', 0),
(75, 1, 'Order processing procedure has been improved', '&lt;p&gt;In order to make the orders to be managed more easily, our orders support team spent about 24 hours to settle all of the current orders. Now the orders are more orderly and conveniently, all the orders can be sent out in a short time if there are enough stock. Moreover, our tech team are trying their best to develop a new order management system, to improve our order processing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-15 09:18:59', 0),
(76, 1, 'New promotion is planing to release for Thanksgiving Day!', '&lt;p&gt;Thanksgiving Day is coming. Our marketing department are busy with the preparation for the Thanksgiving Day campagin. All of the customers can get big discount from this promotion. Please pay close attention to our &quot;Special Offers&quot; page to get the latest information about it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-19 09:19:42', 0),
(77, 1, 'Thanksgiving Day promotion was released in advance.', '&lt;p&gt;Thanksgiving Day is a festival that express our thanks to the people who helped us. We would like to sincere thank all the customers who gave great support on Lively 24*7 Service this year. And during Thanksgiving Day period, we like to offer super discount for all the old and new customers in return: Up to 98% discount off for Lively 24*7 Service product. For more details, please refer to the &quot;Special Offers&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-20 09:21:03', 0),
(78, 1, 'Happy ThanksGiving!', '&lt;p&gt;On behalf of every one at Lively 24*7 Service, we wish you and your loved ones happiness this holiday.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-22 09:24:00', 0),
(79, 1, 'Some products changed in &quot;Special Offer&quot; due to lack of stock.', '&lt;p&gt;Some products are too hot and no stock left at present, we add new products to replace them. But all the products are also limited, if you are to buy some at such low price, please hurry up, don''t miss it!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-24 09:24:29', 0),
(80, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support team are having meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. Our 24*7 sales support will be offline from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8), and technical support team will be offline from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8). If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@livelyservice.com&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;support@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes.&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot; /&gt;\r\nSorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-26 09:26:03', 0),
(81, 1, 'The last 24 hours for you to get Thanksgiving Day Special Offers', '&lt;p&gt;We will end this special offers within the next 24 hours. If you are to buy any product from Lively 24*7 Service, please hurry up! Time is limited, don''t miss it!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-26 09:27:54', 0),
(82, 1, 'Introduce your friends, Get free PVAs from us', '&lt;p&gt;We are providing $9 for Facebook FriendAdeder life time license along with 10 free PVAs for new customers at present. If you have any friends want to follow the example of you succeeded in Facebook marketing, we''d appreciated very much if you could introduce them to have a look at this special offer.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMeanwhile, as the return, you are entitled to get 10 free PVAs once you recommended our service to a new customer successfully. For more deatils, please refer to &quot;Special Offers&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-29 09:29:15', 0),
(83, 1, 'The beta verison of Carousel View in Lively 24*7 Service website has been released', '&lt;p&gt;The beta verison of Carousel View was released in Lively 24*7 Service website. Customers can find the latest special offers and useful information easily from the top carousel view from now on. Hope it can help you find your favorite page or service directly and conveniently.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-11-30 09:29:54', 0),
(84, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support team are having meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. Our 24*7 sales support will be offline from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8), and technical support team will be offline from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8). If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@livelyservice.com&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;support@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-03 09:30:29', 0),
(85, 1, 'The &quot;Affiliate Program&quot; page was updated', '&lt;p&gt;Our sales department modified some related information about the &quot;Affiliate Program&quot;, make the description and working flow of affiliate more clearly and easier to understand. For more details about our Affiliate Program, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/affiliate_program.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-05 09:39:16', 0),
(86, 1, 'Facebook FriendAdder Pro 3.0.0 built on 2012.12.07.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;Due to Facebook change, there are still some bugs in features after update on Dec 7, 2012. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get new update. The latest version is Facebook FriendAdder Pro 3.0.0 built on 2012.12.07.01. For more detail about &quot;What''s new&quot; of FFAP, Please click here.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-08 09:41:54', 0),
(87, 1, 'Add the &quot;Affiliate Program&quot; picture in the top Carousel View', '&lt;p&gt;Lively 24*7 Service offers Affiliate Program for all of customers. Easy to join and high commission you can get. If you want to earn some money in your spare time, please hurry up to join us! Just click the carousel view to browse the service page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-11 09:57:24', 0),
(88, 1, 'Service Introduce Videos are seriatim updated', '&lt;p&gt;In order to express our service more clearly, expecially in the working schedule, our support team are developing new videos for each service. In the new service introduce video, you will have a better understanding in our service, and they will be updated once finished.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOf course, if you have any suggestion or question about our service, welcome to contact our 24*7 sales support team in your spare time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-13 09:58:25', 0),
(89, 1, '$9 for FFA life time license will be ended within 24 hours', '&lt;p&gt;The Special Offer for FFA will be ended soon. With this offer, you can get FFA life time license with only $9! And also can get 10 PVAs for free. If you haven''t got FFA, hurry up! Don''t miss this chance!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-19 10:04:12', 0),
(90, 1, 'Free Christmas Present for All Customers', '&lt;p&gt;Thanks a lot for your support to us during the past days. If you have made any order with us before, now you can get a Free Secret Christmas Present from us. For more details, please refer to the &quot;Special Offers&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-20 10:12:13', 0),
(91, 1, '24*7 Re-verification Support Team are on Christmas Holiday from Dec 22nd to Dec 26th', '&lt;p&gt;Christmas Day is coming, our 24*7 Re-verification support team will be offline for four days holiday. That will be caused you can''t bypass mobile phone re-verification successfully with FFA/FFAP during this period. We are very sorry to bring you any trouble, look forward to your understanding and support. Thanks!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHowever, our Lively 24*7 Sales Support Team and Tech Support Team are online during this period. If you have any question or problem, welcome to contact us.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-22 10:17:19', 0),
(92, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Sales Support team are having meeting from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. Our 24*7 sales support will be offline from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8). If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-24 10:21:18', 0),
(93, 1, 'FFA/FFAP Facebook FriendAdder Pro 3.0.0 built on 2012.12.26.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;Our programmer team fixed some bugs in the software caused by the Facebook recent changes. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get new update. The latest version is Facebook FriendAdder (Pro) 3.0.0 built on 2012.12.26.01.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhat''s new in the FFA/FFAP 3.0.0 built on 2012.12.26.01&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI. Features Improved:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Improved: Auto disable the secure browsing option when it''s enabled in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Improved: Detect and bypass some more kinds of unknown login problems in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Bug Fixed:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to get friend number sometimes in &quot;Check Account Information&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to find more others friends to add in &quot;Add Online Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to seperate multiple lines for Mac system in all related features;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-27 10:27:11', 0),
(94, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support Team New Year Holiday Announcement', '&lt;p&gt;We will have our new year holidays from 2012.12.30 16:00 to 2013.1.4 9:00 (GMT+8). Our sales, technical and order support teams will stop working during our holidays. If you need to contact us urgently, please send an email to: support@livelyservice.com.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll the orders which placed during the holidays will be processed when we are back. Sorry for any inconvenient with you. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-12-29 10:29:25', 0),
(95, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support Team are back from holidays', '&lt;p&gt;We are back from our holidays today. All of the regular orders which placed during the holidays will be sent out within 24 hours. We are sorry for the delay and thanks a lot for all of your great support and understanding! Happy New Year to all!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-01-04 10:39:40', 0),
(96, 1, 'Regular Weekly Meeting will be hold from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We will have the weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. All of our support team will be offline during this period. If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-01-07 10:57:29', 0),
(97, 1, '2014 New Year Holiday Announcement news', '&lt;p&gt;We are on New Year holidays from 2013.12.31 17:30 to 2014.1.5 8:30 (GMT+8). For all the orders during our holidays, we will process them when we are back from holidays on 2014.1.5. If you need to contact us urgently, please send an email to:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@livelyservice.com&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); text-decoration:underline; color:#00F;&quot;&gt;support@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;. Sorry for any inconvenient with you. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks and Happy New year!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMoreover, we are providing up to 80% off limited time special offer for you. It will be ended on 2014.01.5. Hurry up! Don''t miss it. For more details, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/2014.html&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-12-31 12:11:33', 0),
(98, 1, 'Merry Christmas!!', '&lt;p&gt;Season''s Greetings with all good wishes for the new year. We wish you the very best in life with love. And to extend our appreciation for your great support, we provide christmas special offers for you. Please do check, don''t miss it! &lt;a href=&quot;http://livelyservice.com/Merrychristmas.html&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:underline; color:#00F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://livelyservice.com/Merrychristmas.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-12-24 14:45:33', 0),
(99, 1, 'Happy Thanksgiving Day!!', '&lt;p&gt;It''s Thanksgiving 2013! Special wishes for a wonderful Thanksgiving with your family and friends!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo express our thanksful for your great support in this year, we are giving away $16,830 special offers as free gifts, don''t miss it! For more details, please refer to &lt;a href=&quot;http://livelyservice.com/Thanksgivingday.html&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:underline; color:#00F;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://livelyservice.com/Thanksgivingday.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-11-28 14:48:19', 0),
(100, 1, 'Add A New Proxy Provider to Our Recomend Proxy List', '&lt;p&gt;PrivateProxy has been checked by our tech support team, and make sure this kind of proxies work well for our facebook software and accounts. So you can safely use for your facebook accounts. For more details about the proxies, please refer to the Private Proxy page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-11-21 14:57:07', 0),
(101, 1, 'A new update of FFA/FFAP has been released', '&lt;p&gt;A new update on fixing some bugs which caused by Facebook recent changes has been released. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get the latest version of FFA/FFAP. The latest new version of is built on 2013.11.15.01. For more detail, please refer to what''s new section in FFA/FFAP service page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-11-15 14:57:45', 0),
(102, 1, 'We are back from our Chinese National Day Holidays', '&lt;p&gt;We are back from our holidays today. All of the regular orders which placed during the holidays have been sent out till now. We are very sorry to cause you any trouble for this delay and thanks for your great support and understanding!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-10-08 14:59:40', 0);
INSERT INTO `mmc_news` (`news_id`, `language_id`, `title`, `text`, `status`, `sort_order`, `date_added`, `user_id`) VALUES
(103, 1, 'Chinese National Day Holiday Announcement', '&lt;p&gt;We are on Chinese National Day holidays from Sept 30th 5:30 PM to Oct 7th 8:30 AM (GMT+8). All orders during our holidays won''t be processed before we are back from holidays.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo express our regret, we are providing almost all our products by 50% discount for all our customers. This special offer will be ended when we are back from holiday. If you need accounts urgently, we highly recommend you place the orders before the holidays, so that you can receive orders in time. For more detail, please check out: http://livelyservice.com/notice.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-29 15:00:12', 0),
(104, 1, 'FFA/FFAP Facebook FriendAdder Pro 4.0.2 built on 2013.09.17.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP/FFA 4.0.2 built on 2013.09.17.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI.Bug Fixed:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to reverify any account in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Bug Fixed: Fixed an unknown error while removing pending friends in &quot;Remove Sent Requests&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to message friends by sex in &quot;Message Online Friends/Message Targeted Friends&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-17 15:01:08', 0),
(105, 1, 'New update of FFA/FFAP has been released', '&lt;p&gt;A new update on fixing some bugs which caused by Facebook recent changes has been released. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get the latest version of FFA/FFAP. The latest new version of is built on 2013.09.16.01. For more detail, please refer to what''s new section in FFA/FFAP service page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-16 15:12:49', 0),
(106, 1, 'Special Offer for Facebook Page Beta Service', '&lt;p&gt;Do you want to start facebook marketing for your product? But the trouble is that you don''t have enough fans/likes to start? We are so excited to tell you that we are providing 2 kinds of Fans/Likes now that can solve your problem.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. &quot;Getting Started Likes&quot; is good for new page. It will make your page looks more popular and credible.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. &quot;Invitations for Real Likes&quot; is good for popular and credible page. It will get 100% real fans/likes to your page and make your page really active.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor more details about this new service, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/special_offers.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-10 15:17:28', 0),
(107, 1, 'Sim Cards Service has been finally released on Setp 3rd', '&lt;p&gt;Sim Cards Service is available for all the FFAP users now. Please upgrade your FFAP to the latest version (FFAP 4.0.0), then run the feature &quot;Verify Non-PVA to PVA&quot; to verify PVAs by yourself with Sim Cards. For more details about this new service, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/sim_cards.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-04 15:18:30', 0),
(108, 1, 'Limited Time Special Offer for FFAP Life Time License', '&lt;p&gt;To celebrate FFAP 4.0.0 comes out, we have determined to provide some more life time licenses for our customers which we have stopped selling since 2012. Only $299 for Life Time License now! However, this is a Limited Time Special Offer, only available from Sept 1st to Sept 8th. Hurry Up, Don''t Miss It! http://www.livelyservice.com/special_offers.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-02 15:19:50', 0),
(109, 1, 'FFAP 4.0.0 Beta License has been expired', '&lt;p&gt;All the FFAP 4.0.0 Beta Lincens are not available since FFAP 4.0.0 final version released. But for the FFAP 3.0.0 users, you can upgrade your software to 4.0.0 version automatically.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-02 08:20:40', 0),
(110, 1, 'Facebook FriendAdder Pro (FFAP) 4.0.0 has been released on 2013.09.01', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP 4.0.0&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNew Feature:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. New Feature: Add a new feature called &quot;Verify Non-PVA to PVA&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. New Feature: Add a new feature called &quot;Unverify PVA to Non-PVA&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. New Feature: Add a new feature called &quot;Unlock Friend Photo Block&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. New Feature: Add a new feature called &quot;Monitor Account Status&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. New Feature: Add a new option called &quot;Followers&quot; in &quot;Find Targeted Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. New Feature: Add a new option called &quot;Group&quot; in &quot;Invite Account Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. New Feature: Add a new option called &quot;Page&quot; in &quot;Invite Account Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. New Feature: Add a new new type to &quot;Share a Link&quot; in &quot;Post Wall Updates&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n9. New Feature: Add a new new type to &quot;Upload a Photo&quot; in &quot;Post Wall Updates&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Features Improved:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Improved: Add campaign info for &quot;Account&quot; field in all releated features;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Improved: Update software LOGO, splash image and FFAP features view;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-09-01 15:21:45', 0),
(111, 1, 'We have put off the day to officially release FFAP 4.0.0.', '&lt;p&gt;The official version of FFAP 4.0.0 is postponed to be released on 2013.09.01. If you have any suggestions, feature requests and other opinions about FFAP, welcome to contact our technical support team. In addition, buying one copy of Yearly License of FFAP 3.0.0, you will get one license of FFAP 4.0.0 Beta for free. You can experience new features in FFAP 4.0.0 Beta before it is officially released.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-08-02 15:28:00', 0),
(112, 1, 'Party Time Notice In Advance', '&lt;p&gt;We will have a party time from August 2nd 17:30 to August 5th 8:30 AM(GMT +8) this week. Our support team will not work during this time. If you have any questions about our product or service, welcome to contact our 24*7 support team before our holiday. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-07-30 15:28:53', 0),
(113, 1, 'Important notice for the customers who use Yahoo or AIM', '&lt;p&gt;We have cancelled Yahoo and AIM contact ways. Customers in Yahoo or AIM can add our support team by skype or email for help. For more details, please refer to http://www.livelyservice.com/contact_us.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-07-22 15:29:30', 0),
(114, 1, 'A new update of FFAP 4.0.0 Beta has been released', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 built on 2013.07.09.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI. Features Improved:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Improved: Detect and bypass some more kinds of login problems in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Bug Fixed:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to verify accounts sometimes in &quot;Verify Non-PVA to PVA&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to report added friends in &quot;Upload Contact File&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-07-10 15:30:57', 0),
(115, 1, 'New beta service was released', '&lt;p&gt;We have added FFAP 4.0.0 (Beta) service and Sim Cards (Beta) service on the left navigation bar of Lively 24*7 Service website.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you want to know what’s new feature in FFAP 4.0.0 Beta version and the tutorial video of new features, please do check out http://www.livelyservice.com/ffap_beta.html. Sim Cards service is provided real mobile phone number to help you to verify your accounts as PVA. This Service is still under testing. For more details, please refer to http://www.livelyservice.com/sim_cards.html.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-18 15:34:41', 0),
(116, 1, 'Create PVA by yourself with FFAP 4.0.0 Beta', '&lt;p&gt;We are providing limited special offers for All-In-One Testing Package. Pay just $9 to buy 10 Non-PVA and get FFAP 4.0.0 beta and 10 Sim Cards for free.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor more detail, please do check out: http://livelyservice.com/beta.html. There are only a limited number of copies! Hurry Up...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-18 08:37:53', 0),
(117, 1, 'A new update of FFA/FFAP has been released', '&lt;p&gt;Our programmer team fixed some bugs in the software caused by the Facebook recent changes. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get new update. The latest version is Facebook FriendAdder (Pro) 3.0.0 built on 2013.06.17.01&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhat''s new in FFA/FFAP 3.0.0 built on 2013.06.17.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Improved: Detect and bypass some more kinds of login problems in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to check friend number in &quot;Check Account Information&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-17 15:41:19', 0),
(118, 1, 'FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 built on 2013.06.17.01 was released', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 built on 2013.06.17.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI. Features Improved:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Improved: Detect and bypass some more kinds of login problems in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Improved: Add a new option to find account added friends first in &quot;Unlock Friend Photo Block&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Bug Fixed:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to check friend number in &quot;Check Account Information&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2, Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to check account status in &quot;Monitor Account Status&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-17 15:42:41', 0),
(119, 1, 'Dragon Boat Festival Holiday Announcement', '&lt;p&gt;We are sorry to notice you that we will be on Chinese Dragon Boat Festival holidays from June 11th 5:30 PM to June 12th 6:00 PM (GMT +8). If you want to contact us during the holidays, please feel free to email support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as possible when we are back. Thank you for your understanding and patience.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrders of our service which are placed during our holidays will not be processed before we are back from holiday on June 13th. However, we would like to release our holiday special offers (up to 90% off) for you in advice. so that you can get the special offers and receive your orders to keep your work going on without any stop.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor more details, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/DragonBoatFestival.html.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-09 15:45:16', 0),
(120, 1, 'Party Time Notice', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a party this weekend. All our support teams do not work from June 1st 17:30 to June 2nd 09:00 AM(GMT +8). We are sorry for the inconvenience. If you have any questions, please feel free to email support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as possible when we are back. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-06-01 15:48:31', 0),
(121, 1, 'A new update of FFAP has been released on 29th, May', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 built on 2013.05.29.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to check account status in &quot;Monitor Account Status&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to add friends by sex in &quot;Add Online Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to add friends by sex in &quot;Add Targeted Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to message friends by sex in &quot;Message Online Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to message friends by sex in &quot;Message Targeted Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to find more friends by keywards in &quot;Find Targeted Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to find more walls by keywards in &quot;Find Targeted Walls&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to invite any friend to pages in &quot;Invite Account Friends&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n9. Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to find and add any friend in &quot;Upload Contact File&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-05-29 15:52:37', 0),
(122, 1, 'Weekly meeting is canceled', '&lt;p&gt;Our 24*7 Sales support team usually has a weekly meeting on Monday from 3PM to 5PM.The weekly meeting is canceled now. If you have any question during this time, please feel free to contact us.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-05-13 15:58:59', 0),
(123, 1, 'We are back from May Day Holidays', '&lt;p&gt;All Lively 24*7 Service support teams are back from holiday. All of the regular orders which placed during the holidays will be delivered as soon as possible. We are very sorry to cause you any trouble for this delay and thanks for your great support and understanding!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMoreover, the May Day Special Offers will be ended very soon, so if you haven''t got these special offers yet, hurry up!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-05-05 15:59:40', 0),
(124, 1, '&quot;Subscribe Mobile Phone Number&quot; will be updated', '&lt;p&gt;As we can get longer valid period Chinese SIM card, we scheduled to charge this service by yearly. The price will reduce to $50 per year. With this service, it can help you to verify your account with a phone number and bypass re-verification roadblock at any time with zero cost during the rental period.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-04-29 16:03:46', 0),
(125, 1, 'May Day Holiday Announcement', '&lt;p&gt;We are sorry to notice you that all LivelyService support teams will be on May Day holiday from April 30th 5:00 PM to May 5th 8:30 AM (GMT +8). If you have any questions, you can send emails to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as we are back. Thank you for your understanding and patience.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMoreover, we are providing up to 90% off special offers for our products during our holidays. For more details, please refer to http://www.livelyservice.com/May_Day.html.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-24 16:04:23', 0),
(126, 1, '24*7 Sales Support Team have the Weekly Meeting from 4PM to 5PM', '&lt;p&gt;24*7 Sales Support Team will be offline for one hour from 4PM to 5PM. If you have any questions during this period, please just leave message on instant messengers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. They will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-22 16:05:02', 0),
(127, 1, 'A new update of FFA/FFAP has been released', '&lt;p&gt;A new update on fixing some bugs which caused by Facebook recent changes has been released. Please click &quot;Help&quot;--&amp;gt; &quot;Find Updates Now&quot; to get the latest version of FFA/FFAP. The latest new version of is built on 2013.04.19.01. For more detail, please refer to what''s new section in FFA/FFAP service page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-19 16:05:49', 0),
(128, 1, 'The &quot;Affiliate Program&quot; page was updated', '&lt;p&gt;Our affiliate team has modified some related information about the &quot;Affiliate Program&quot;. If you have any questions, please check the FAQ section. For more details about our Affiliate Program, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/affiliate_program.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-16 16:06:21', 0),
(129, 1, 'Lively 24*7 Service Support team are having meeting from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8)', '&lt;p&gt;We are having a weekly meeting from 3PM to 5PM. Our 24*7 sales support will be offline from 4PM to 5PM (GMT+8), and technical support team will be offline from 3PM to 5PM (GMT+8). If you have any question during this time, please leave us message on instant messengers, or send email to support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as the meeting finishes. Sorry to cause you any trouble. Looking forward to your understanding and support. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-15 16:06:54', 0),
(130, 1, ' The &quot;Affiliate Program&quot; page will be updated soon', '&lt;p&gt;To make affiliates have a clear understanding of Lively 24*7 Service affiliate programs, our affiliate team are modifying the &quot;Affiliate Program&quot; page. It will be added &quot;working flow&quot; and &quot;FAQ&quot; sections. If you have any questions about affiliate program, you could check it out through the &quot;FAQ&quot; section firstly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-10 16:07:29', 0),
(131, 1, 'We are back from our Qing Ming Festival Holidays', '&lt;p&gt;We are back from our holidays today. All of the regular orders which placed during the holidays will be sent out within 24 hours. We are very sorry to cause you any trouble for this delay and thanks for your great support and understanding!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-06 16:08:05', 0),
(132, 1, 'Qing Ming Festival Holiday Announcement', '&lt;p&gt;We are sorry to notice you that we are on Chinese Qing Ming Festival holidays from April 3rd 5:00 PM to April 6th 8:30 AM (GMT +8). All of our support team are not on work during this period, so all the orders that are placed during our holidays will be processed as soon as we are back to work. If you want to contact us during the holidays, please feel free to email support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as possible when we are back. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMoreover, we are providing special offers for our products during our holidays. Joining our VIP Program will help you get more discount. For more detail about our VIP program, please refer to: http://livelyservice.com/vip.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-03 16:08:42', 0),
(133, 1, 'Important notice for the customers who use MSN messager', '&lt;p&gt;Since MSN has been finally shut down by Microsoft on 15 March 2013, so we won''t login our MSN anymore. Customers in MSN can add our 24*7 support team by skype (livelyservice) for help.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-04-02 16:09:21', 0),
(134, 1, 'Qingming Festival Holiday Announce In Advance', '&lt;p&gt;We will have a two days holiday from April 3rd to April 5th next week. Our support team will not work during this period. If you have any questions about our product or service, welcome to contact our 24*7 support team before our holiday. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-03-29 16:09:54', 0),
(135, 1, 'FFAP 3.0.0 is just updated with some problems fixed', '&lt;p&gt;What''s new in FFAP 3.0.0 built on 2013.03.27.01:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) Improved: Detect and bypass some more kinds of roadblock in &quot;Bypass Login Problems&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to check all proxies in &quot;Manage Proxies&quot;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3) Bug Fixed: Fixed a problem of failed to share photos in &quot;Share Wall Updates&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2013-03-27 16:10:32', 0),
(136, 1, 'FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 has been released on Mar 18th', '&lt;p&gt;We have released the FFAP 4.0.0 Beta 1 for beta testers yesterday. The final version of FFAP 4.0.0 is scheduled to be released on 2013.07.01. Now we would like to give away some free beta testing licenses for our customers to join our beta testing group. If you would like to get one testing copy, please refer to http://livelyservice.com/beta.html&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2014-03-07 16:11:21', 0);
